{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Dubinsky attacked immediately Caldwell, and told him, look, you are a socialist?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't accept Jews into this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Caldwell told him that is a lie.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, look, he said, it's not a lie, because we have the information from Germany-- we know it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said give me a list of 100 Jewish families, and I will see that they come on this list.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they sent to us-- to Germany for the list, and I was put as number one, on top of the list.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the mean time, I got the permits that I never used it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I am only telling you how the situation was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on, I remember we had a party in Junkers' house for the general director of UNRRA for Europe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I forgot his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was, during the war, the general director of the American Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later, after the war, he was general director of UNRRA for Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when Masaryk was-- when Jan Maseryk, Maseryk was killed, the foreign minister, thrown out through the window, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] he was the director there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He gave his papers, and the papers of few of his staff, to a number of people-- Jews, mostly-- and they escaped Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This, few months later, came out and the Czechoslovakian government started protests in Washington.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was recalled from Europe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was a party for him before he was going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was sitting at of the garden party with the military governor for the region, and his girlfriend, and my wife.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came to me and asking, Manny, what is going on with you?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When are we leaving?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, as a matter of fact, I have the permits.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
